mariadb -h 127.0.0.1 -P 9001 -u root -p mydatabase


docker run -p 9001:3306 db_server


*
* PYTEST
*
* Run pytest with smoke marker
*
# pytest tests/ -m smoke
====================================== 1 passed, 3 deselected in 4.04s 

*
* Run pytest with a specific test name
*
# pytest tests/test_docker_mariadb.py::test_create_table
============================================= 1 passed in 0.45s

*
* Run tests by keyword expressions
*
# pytest -k "create"
====================================== 1 passed, 3 deselected in 0.70s =======================================
